answers.answer: this morning I rushed to the primary doctor's office, she use the dipstick to get the trace AGAIN!So how come the microalbumin normal but albumin abnormal. My doctor think it is not a big issue, but I am obsessed by this trace protein.

title: urine protein trace but microalbumin in normal range
